{"number":138,"verseCount":60,"verses":[[1,["On the third of October, in the year nineteen hundred and eighteen, I ",["",287],"sat in my room ",["pondering",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Meditation","tg/meditation"],"; ",["Scriptures, Study of","tg/scriptures-study-of"],"."]]]," over the scriptures;"]],[2,["And ",["reflecting",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—H 1:12","pgp/js-h/1.12"],"."]]]," upon the great ",["atoning",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 20:28","nt/matt/20.28"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"."]]]," ",["sacrifice",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Sacrifice","tg/sacrifice"],"."]]]," that was made by the Son of God, for the ",["redemption",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Redemption","tg/redemption"],"."]]]," of the world;"]],[3,["And the great and wonderful ",["love",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 3:16 (14–17)","nt/john/3.16"],". ",["TG God, Love of","tg/god-love-of"],"."]]]," made manifest by the Father and the Son in the coming of the ",["Redeemer",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 63:9 (1–9)","ot/isa/63.9"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"."]]]," into the world;"]],[4,["That through his ",["atonement",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 25:23","bofm/2-ne/25.23"],"; ",["A of F 1:3","pgp/a-of-f/1.3"],"."]]],", and by ",["obedience",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 7:21 (21–27)","nt/matt/7.21"],". ",["TG Obedience","tg/obedience"],"."]]]," to the principles of the gospel, mankind might be saved."]],[5,["While I was thus engaged, my mind reverted to the writings of the apostle Peter, to the ",["primitive saints",["study-note-ref","a",["IE former-day saints."]]]," scattered abroad throughout ",["Pontus",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Pet. 1:1","nt/1-pet/1.1"],"."]]],", Galatia, Cappadocia, and other parts of Asia, where the gospel had been ",["preached",["study-note-ref","c",[["Acts 16:6 (6–9)","nt/acts/16.6"],"; ",["19:26 (10–26)","nt/acts/19.26"],"."]]]," after the crucifixion of the Lord."]],[6,["I opened the Bible and read the ",["third",["study-note-ref","a",["See ",["1 Pet. 3:18–20","nt/1-pet/3.18-20"]," and ",["4:6","nt/1-pet/4.6"]," in the New Testament for additional notes and cross-references."]]]," and fourth chapters of the first epistle of Peter, and as I read I was greatly ",["impressed",["study-note-ref","b",[["JS—H 1:12 (11–13)","pgp/js-h/1.12"],"."]]],", more than I had ever been before, with the following passages:"]],[7,["“For Christ also hath once suffered for sins, the just for the unjust, that he might bring us to God, being put to death in the flesh, but quickened by the Spirit:"]],[8,["“By which also he went and preached unto the spirits in ",["prison",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 61:1 (1–2)","ot/isa/61.1"],"; ",["Luke 4:18 (18–21)","nt/luke/4.18"],"; ",["D&C 76:73 (73–74)","dc-testament/dc/76.73"],"; ",["88:99","dc-testament/dc/88.99"],"."]]],";"]],[9,["“Which sometime were disobedient, when once the longsuffering of God waited in the days of Noah, while the ark was a preparing, wherein few, that is, eight souls were saved by water.” (",["1 Peter 3:18–20",["scripture-ref"]],".)"]],[10,["“For for this cause was the gospel preached also to them that are dead, that they might be judged according to men in the flesh, but live according to God in the spirit.” (",["1 Peter 4:6",["scripture-ref"]],".)"]],[11,["As I ",["pondered",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 76:19","dc-testament/dc/76.19"],"."]]]," over these things which are ",["written",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Scriptures, Value of","tg/scriptures-value-of"],"."]]],", the ",["eyes",["study-note-ref","c",[["Luke 24:31","nt/luke/24.31"],"; ",["Eph. 1:18","nt/eph/1.18"],"; ",["D&C 76:12 (10, 12, 19)","dc-testament/dc/76.12"],"; ",["110:1","dc-testament/dc/110.1"],"."]]]," of my ",["understanding",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Understanding","tg/understanding"],"."]]]," were opened, and the Spirit of the Lord ",["rested",["study-note-ref","e",[["Num. 11:25","ot/num/11.25"],"; ",["Isa. 11:2","ot/isa/11.2"],"."]]]," upon me, and I saw the hosts of the ",["dead",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Spirits, Disembodied","tg/spirits-disembodied"],"."]]],", both small and great."]],[12,["And there were gathered together in one place an innumerable company of the spirits of the ",["just",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ezek. 18:9 (5–9)","ot/ezek/18.9"],"; ",["D&C 76:69 (69–70)","dc-testament/dc/76.69"],"."]]],", who had been ",["faithful",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 6:13","dc-testament/dc/6.13"],"; ",["51:19","dc-testament/dc/51.19"],"; ",["76:52 (51–53)","dc-testament/dc/76.52"],"."]]]," in the ",["testimony",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Testimony","tg/testimony"],"."]]]," of Jesus while they lived in mortality;"]],[13,["And who had offered ",["sacrifice",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sacrifice","tg/sacrifice"],"."]]]," in the ",["similitude",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation","tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Types of, in Memory","tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-memory"],"."]]]," of the great sacrifice of the Son of God, and had suffered ",["tribulation",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Persecution","tg/persecution"],"; ",["Tribulation","tg/tribulation"],"."]]]," in their Redeemer’s ",["name",["study-note-ref","d",[["Matt. 5:11 (10–12)","nt/matt/5.11"],"."]]],"."]],[14,["All these had departed the mortal life, firm in the ",["hope",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Cor. 15:19 (18–21)","nt/1-cor/15.19"],"; ",["Ether 12:4","bofm/ether/12.4"],"; ",["Moro. 7:41 (3, 40–48)","bofm/moro/7.41"],"."]]]," of a glorious ",["resurrection",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Resurrection","tg/resurrection"],"."]]],", through the ",["grace",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]]," of God the ",["Father",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"."]]]," and his ",["Only Begotten Son",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"."]]],", Jesus Christ."]],[15,["I beheld that they were filled with ",["joy",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 51:11","ot/isa/51.11"],"; ",["Alma 40:12 (11–13)","bofm/alma/40.12"],"."]]]," and gladness, and were rejoicing together because the day of their ",["deliverance",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]]," was at hand."]],[16,["They were assembled awaiting the advent of the Son of God into the ",["spirit world",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 23:43","nt/luke/23.43"],"; ",["Alma 40:20 (20–21)","bofm/alma/40.20"],". ",["TG Paradise","tg/paradise"],"."]]],", to declare their ",["redemption",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Redemption","tg/redemption"],"."]]]," from the ",["bands",["study-note-ref","c",[["Alma 36:18","bofm/alma/36.18"],"; ",["Morm. 9:13","bofm/morm/9.13"],"."]]]," of death."]],[17,["Their sleeping ",["dust",["study-note-ref","a",[["Job 34:15","ot/job/34.15"],"."]]]," was to be ",["restored",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Ne. 9:13 (10–13)","bofm/2-ne/9.13"],"; ",["Alma 41:4 (3–5)","bofm/alma/41.4"],"."]]]," unto its ",["perfect",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Perfection","tg/perfection"],"."]]]," frame, ",["bone",["study-note-ref","d",[["Ezek. 37:7 (1–14)","ot/ezek/37.7"],"."]]]," to his bone, and the sinews and the flesh upon them, the ",["spirit",["study-note-ref","e",[["D&C 93:33 (33–34)","dc-testament/dc/93.33"],"."]]]," and the body to be united never again to be divided, that they might receive a fulness of ",["joy",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]],"."]],[18,["While this vast multitude waited and conversed, rejoicing in the hour of their ",["deliverance",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 9:12","bofm/2-ne/9.12"],"."]]]," from the chains of death, the Son of God appeared, declaring ",["liberty",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"; ",["Salvation for the Dead","tg/salvation-for-the-dead"],"."]]]," to the ",["captives",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 61:1","ot/isa/61.1"],"."]]]," who had been faithful;"]],[19,["And there he ",["preached",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 76:73 (72–74)","dc-testament/dc/76.73"],". ",["TG Preaching","tg/preaching"],"."]]]," to them the everlasting ",["gospel",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Gospel","tg/gospel"],"."]]],", the doctrine of the ",["resurrection",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 9:13 (4–22)","bofm/2-ne/9.13"],"."]]]," and the redemption of mankind from the ",["fall",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Fall of Man","tg/fall-of-man"],"."]]],", and from individual sins on conditions of ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]],"."]],[20,["But unto the ",["wicked",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 40:14 (13–14)","bofm/alma/40.14"],". ",["TG Spirits in Prison","tg/spirits-in-prison"],"; ",["Wickedness","tg/wickedness"],"."]]]," he did not go, and among the ungodly and the unrepentant who had ",["defiled",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Ne. 10:21","bofm/1-ne/10.21"],"; ",["D&C 138:37","dc-testament/dc/138.37"],"; ",["Moses 6:57","pgp/moses/6.57"],"."]]]," themselves while in the flesh, his voice was not raised;"]],[21,["Neither did the ",["rebellious",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 23:37","nt/matt/23.37"],". ",["TG Rebellion","tg/rebellion"],"."]]]," who rejected the ",["testimonies",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 76:82","dc-testament/dc/76.82"],"."]]]," and the warnings of the ancient ",["prophets",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Prophets, Rejection of","tg/prophets-rejection-of"],"."]]]," behold his ",["presence",["study-note-ref","d",[["Moses 6:57","pgp/moses/6.57"],"."]]],", nor look upon his face."]],[22,["Where these were, ",["darkness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Darkness, Spiritual","tg/darkness-spiritual"],"."]]]," reigned, but among the righteous there was ",["peace",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Peace of God","tg/peace-of-god"],"."]]],";"]],[23,["And the saints rejoiced in their ",["redemption",["study-note-ref","a",[["Heb. 9:12 (11–15)","nt/heb/9.12"],". ",["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"; ",["Redemption","tg/redemption"],"."]]],", and bowed the ",["knee",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 14:11","nt/rom/14.11"],"; ",["Mosiah 27:31","bofm/mosiah/27.31"],"."]]]," and acknowledged the Son of God as their Redeemer and Deliverer from death and the ",["chains",["study-note-ref","c",[["Alma 5:7","bofm/alma/5.7"],"."]]]," of ",["hell",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Hell","tg/hell"],"."]]],"."]],[24,["Their countenances ",["shone",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ex. 34:30 (29–30, 35)","ot/ex/34.30"],"; ",["Hel. 5:36 (23–48)","bofm/hel/5.36"],"; ",["JS—H 1:32 (31–32)","pgp/js-h/1.32"],". ",["TG Light [noun]","tg/light-noun"],"."]]],", and the ",["radiance",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 104:2","ot/ps/104.2"],"; ",["Isa. 60:19","ot/isa/60.19"],"; ",["Rev. 22:5","nt/rev/22.5"],"; ",["JS—H 1:17","pgp/js-h/1.17"],"."]]]," from the presence of the Lord rested upon them, and they ",["sang",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Chr. 29:30","ot/2-chr/29.30"],". ",["TG Singing","tg/singing"],"; ",["Worship","tg/worship"],"."]]]," praises unto his holy name."]],[25,["I marveled, for I understood that the Savior spent about three years in his ",["ministry",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"."]]]," among the Jews and those of the house of Israel, endeavoring to ",["teach",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Teaching","tg/teaching"],"."]]]," them the everlasting gospel and call them unto repentance;"]],[26,["And yet, notwithstanding his mighty works, and miracles, and proclamation of the truth, in great ",["power",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 11:28 (28, 31)","bofm/1-ne/11.28"],"."]]]," and authority, there were but ",["few",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 7:14 (13–14)","nt/matt/7.14"],"; ",["1 Ne. 11:31 (28–32)","bofm/1-ne/11.31"],"; ",["14:12","bofm/1-ne/14.12"],"."]]]," who hearkened to his voice, and rejoiced in his presence, and received salvation at his hands."]],[27,["But his ministry among those who were dead was limited to the ",["brief",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mark 8:31","nt/mark/8.31"],"."]]]," time intervening between the crucifixion and his resurrection;"]],[28,["And I wondered at the words of Peter—wherein he said that the Son of God preached unto the ",["spirits",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Spirits in Prison","tg/spirits-in-prison"],"."]]]," in prison, who sometime were disobedient, when once the long-suffering of God waited in the days of Noah—and how it was possible for him to preach to those spirits and perform the necessary labor among them in so short a time."]],[29,["And as I wondered, my eyes were opened, and my understanding ",["quickened",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 76:12","dc-testament/dc/76.12"],"."]]],", and I perceived that the Lord went not in person among the ",["wicked",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 138:20","dc-testament/dc/138.20"],"."]]]," and the disobedient who had rejected the truth, to teach them;"]],[30,["But behold, from among the righteous, he ",["organized",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven","tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"],"."]]]," his forces and appointed ",["messengers",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"."]]],", ",["clothed",["study-note-ref","c",[["Luke 24:49","nt/luke/24.49"],". ",["TG Delegation of Responsibility","tg/delegation-of-responsibility"],"; ",["Priesthood, Authority","tg/priesthood-authority"],"; ",["Priesthood, Power of","tg/priesthood-power-of"],"."]]]," with power and authority, and ",["commissioned",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 20:73","dc-testament/dc/20.73"],"."]]]," them to go forth and carry the light of the gospel to them that were in ",["darkness",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Darkness, Spiritual","tg/darkness-spiritual"],"."]]],", even to ",["all",["study-note-ref","f",[["D&C 1:2 (2, 11)","dc-testament/dc/1.2"],"."]]]," the spirits of men; and thus was the gospel preached to the dead."]],[31,["And the chosen messengers went forth to declare the ",["acceptable",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 61:2","ot/isa/61.2"],"; ",["Luke 4:19","nt/luke/4.19"],"."]]]," day of the Lord and proclaim ",["liberty",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Liberty","tg/liberty"],"."]]]," to the captives who were bound, even unto all who would ",["repent",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Repent","tg/repent"],"; ",["Teachable","tg/teachable"],"."]]]," of their sins and receive the gospel."]],[32,["Thus was the gospel preached to those who had ",["died",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 8:24 (21–24)","nt/john/8.24"],"."]]]," in their sins, without a ",["knowledge",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 128:5","dc-testament/dc/128.5"],". ",["TG Knowledge","tg/knowledge"],"."]]]," of the truth, or in ",["transgression",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Transgress","tg/transgress"],"."]]],", having ",["rejected",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 76:74 (73–74)","dc-testament/dc/76.74"],"."]]]," the prophets."]],[33,["These were taught ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["A of F 1:4","pgp/a-of-f/1.4"],". ",["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]]," in God, repentance from sin, ",["vicarious baptism",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 124:33 (28–39)","dc-testament/dc/124.33"],". ",["TG Baptism, Essential","tg/baptism-essential"],"; ",["Baptism for the Dead","tg/baptism-for-the-dead"],"."]]]," for the ",["remission",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Remission of Sins","tg/remission-of-sins"],"."]]]," of sins, the ",["gift",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Holy Ghost, Gift of","tg/holy-ghost-gift-of"],"."]]]," of the Holy Ghost by the laying on of hands,"]],[34,["And all other principles of the gospel that were necessary for them to know in order to qualify themselves that they might be ",["judged",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Pet. 4:6","nt/1-pet/4.6"],". ",["TG Judgment, the Last","tg/judgment-the-last"],"; ",["Justice","tg/justice"],"."]]]," according to men in the flesh, but live according to God in the spirit."]],[35,["And so it was made known among the dead, both small and great, the unrighteous as well as the faithful, that redemption had been wrought through the ",["sacrifice",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 34:14 (9–16)","bofm/alma/34.14"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"; ",["Sacrifice","tg/sacrifice"],"."]]]," of the Son of God upon the ",["cross",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of","tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"],"."]]],"."]],[36,["Thus was it made known that our Redeemer spent his time during his sojourn in the world of ",["spirits",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Paradise","tg/paradise"],"."]]],", instructing and preparing the faithful spirits of the ",["prophets",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Prophets, Mission of","tg/prophets-mission-of"],"."]]]," who had testified of him in the flesh;"]],[37,["That they might carry the message of redemption unto all the dead, unto whom he could not go personally, because of their ",["rebellion",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 10:21","bofm/1-ne/10.21"],"; ",["D&C 138:20","dc-testament/dc/138.20"],"; ",["Moses 6:57","pgp/moses/6.57"],"."]]]," and transgression, that they through the ministration of his servants might also hear his words."]],[38,["Among the great and ",["mighty",["study-note-ref","a",[["Abr. 3:22 (22–26)","pgp/abr/3.22"],"."]]]," ones who were assembled in this vast congregation of the righteous were Father ",["Adam",["study-note-ref","b",[["Moses 1:34","pgp/moses/1.34"],". ",["TG Adam","tg/adam"],"."]]],", the ",["Ancient of Days",["study-note-ref","c",[["Dan. 7:9 (9–14)","ot/dan/7.9"],"; ",["2 Ne. 2:20","bofm/2-ne/2.20"],"; ",["D&C 27:11","dc-testament/dc/27.11"],"."]]]," and father of all,"]],[39,["And our glorious ",["Mother",["study-note-ref","a",[["Moses 4:26","pgp/moses/4.26"],"."]]]," ",["Eve",["study-note-ref","b",[["Gen. 3:20","ot/gen/3.20"],"; ",["Moses 5:12 (4, 11–12)","pgp/moses/5.12"],"."]]],", with many of her faithful ",["daughters",["study-note-ref","c",[["Moses 5:2 (2–3)","pgp/moses/5.2"],". ",["TG Sons and Daughters of God","tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"],"; ",["Woman","tg/woman"],"."]]]," who had lived through the ages and worshiped the true and living God."]],[40,[["Abel",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gen. 4:2 (1–8)","ot/gen/4.2"],"; ",["Moses 5:17 (17–32)","pgp/moses/5.17"],"."]]],", the first ",["martyr",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Martyrdom","tg/martyrdom"],"."]]],", was there, and his brother ",["Seth",["study-note-ref","c",[["Gen. 4:25 (25–26)","ot/gen/4.25"],"; ",["Moses 6:3 (2–13)","pgp/moses/6.3"],"."]]],", one of the mighty ones, who was in the express ",["image",["study-note-ref","d",[["Gen. 5:3","ot/gen/5.3"],"; ",["Moses 6:10","pgp/moses/6.10"],"."]]]," of his father, Adam."]],[41,[["Noah",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gen. 6:8 (1–22)","ot/gen/6.8"],"; ",["Moses 8:13 (8–30)","pgp/moses/8.13"],"."]]],", who gave warning of the ",["",290],"flood; ",["Shem",["study-note-ref","b",[["Gen. 5:32","ot/gen/5.32"],"."]]],", the great ",["high priest",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG High Priest, Melchizedek Priesthood","tg/high-priest-melchizedek-priesthood"],"; ",["Priesthood, Melchizedek","tg/priesthood-melchizedek"],"."]]],"; ",["Abraham",["study-note-ref","d",[["Gen. 17:5 (1–27)","ot/gen/17.5"],"."]]],", the father of the faithful; ",["Isaac",["study-note-ref","e",[["Gen. 21:3 (1–8)","ot/gen/21.3"],"."]]],", ",["Jacob",["study-note-ref","f",[["Gen. 35:10 (1–29)","ot/gen/35.10"],"."]]],", and Moses, the great ",["law-giver",["study-note-ref","g",[["TG Law of Moses","tg/law-of-moses"],"."]]]," of Israel;"]],[42,["And ",["Isaiah",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 1:1","ot/isa/1.1"],"."]]],", who declared by prophecy that the Redeemer was anointed to bind up the broken-hearted, to proclaim liberty to the ",["captives",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 61:1 (1–2)","ot/isa/61.1"],"."]]],", and the opening of the ",["prison",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Spirits in Prison","tg/spirits-in-prison"],"."]]]," to them that were bound, were also there."]],[43,["Moreover, Ezekiel, who was shown in vision the great valley of ",["dry bones",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ezek. 1:3","ot/ezek/1.3"],"; ",["37:1 (1–14)","ot/ezek/37.1"],"."]]],", whic